صIn Loving Memory of
Rev. Roy Victor Bagley
12.8.33 ~ 29.1.14
Softly the leaves of memory fall,
Gently I gather and treasure then all,
Unseen, unheard,
You are always near,
So missed, So loved, So very dear."ô
